WEBVTT

02:30.040 --> 02:31.560
-Why's someone lying there?
-What's going on?

02:31.640 --> 02:34.440
SEVENTH DAY OF THE TENTH MONTH

02:35.680 --> 02:36.720
What's going on?

02:40.480 --> 02:41.600
Someone's dead!

02:41.680 --> 02:42.800
Someone's dead!

02:44.800 --> 02:45.800
Somebody died!

02:48.240 --> 02:51.040
THE WELL-WOVEN HOUSE

02:53.320 --> 02:54.200
Did you hear?

02:54.280 --> 02:56.160
Last night, they found another body.

02:56.760 --> 02:57.880
<i>So scary!</i>

02:57.960 --> 02:59.560
FOURTEENTH DAY OF THE TENTH MONTH

03:01.760 --> 03:03.760
<i>Again, his heart was ripped out.</i>

03:04.840 --> 03:07.520
I heard a high-ranking demon's here.

03:07.600 --> 03:09.880
So we can't stay in Luo'an anymore.

03:09.960 --> 03:11.560
Now the whole town's in panic.

03:11.640 --> 03:13.600
That demon will keep killing
and taking hearts.

03:14.440 --> 03:16.360
<i>Who knows who'll be next?</i>

03:16.440 --> 03:17.680
<i>How terrifying!</i>

03:17.760 --> 03:19.440
<i>To keep their wedding going,</i>

03:19.520 --> 03:21.560
<i>the Wei family hired a demon hunter</i>
<i>from the Shilin Sect.</i>

03:21.640 --> 03:23.760
-This isn't just any demon hunter.
-Good.

03:23.840 --> 03:25.240
-That's it!
-He has a flower on his forehead!

03:25.320 --> 03:26.200
Good.

03:33.880 --> 03:35.080
Miss, you are…?

03:35.800 --> 03:37.640
I'm the Wei family's bride-to-be's…

03:46.720 --> 03:48.080
cousin.

03:48.160 --> 03:49.040
My name's Yu Wei.

03:50.680 --> 03:51.600
Please, follow me.

03:58.560 --> 04:00.000
WEI QING, HEAD OF THE WEI FAMILY

04:00.080 --> 04:01.080
Here, Shengwei.

04:03.480 --> 04:05.560
YU SHENGWEI, DAUGHTER OF THE YU FAMILY

04:05.640 --> 04:06.760
Master Wei.

04:09.240 --> 04:10.160
LUO WEI, STEWARD OF THE WEI MANSION

04:10.240 --> 04:12.400
The wedding dress
will be done in two days.

04:12.480 --> 04:14.600
I'll deliver it to the Yu mansion myself.

04:15.120 --> 04:17.399
Guess we should go pray
at the Dragon Deity Temple.

04:17.920 --> 04:20.920
May we stay deeply in love
and grow old together.

04:21.000 --> 04:21.920
What do you think?

04:23.280 --> 04:24.280
Come on, Wei Qing.

04:28.760 --> 04:30.440
The Dragon Deity
doesn't handle that stuff.

04:30.520 --> 04:31.360
LIU WEIXUE, WEI QING'S COUSIN

04:31.440 --> 04:32.320
Master Wei.

04:35.120 --> 04:36.480
Miss Yu's cousin has arrived.

04:44.600 --> 04:45.440
You are…?

04:47.160 --> 04:48.520
Shengwei.

04:49.560 --> 04:51.040
I know it's been a while,

04:51.640 --> 04:53.000
but you really don't recognize me?

04:53.760 --> 04:54.960
I'm your cousin,

04:55.840 --> 04:56.960
Yu Wei.

05:01.880 --> 05:02.720
I remember now.

05:04.760 --> 05:05.960
You're Yu Wei.

05:12.040 --> 05:15.960
TWENTY-FOURTH DAY OF THE TENTH MONTH

06:07.440 --> 06:08.520
I've got a hostage now!

06:09.160 --> 06:10.800
Dare you chase me anymore?

06:16.600 --> 06:17.440
Ow, that hurts!

06:35.280 --> 06:36.320
What's your problem?

06:43.640 --> 06:44.480
What kind of weirdo are you?

06:44.560 --> 06:46.640
Why'd you hang me up? Untie me, now!

06:47.240 --> 06:48.720
What's the problem with you demon hunters?

06:48.800 --> 06:51.760
You are not going after that fox demon
who's been killing and stealing hearts.

06:51.840 --> 06:54.160
Why come after me,
an innocent little weasel?

06:54.240 --> 06:55.800
Save it. Get in!

06:56.560 --> 06:58.600
No, please!

07:12.720 --> 07:13.680
Thank you, kind sir,

07:13.760 --> 07:14.960
for saving my life a second time.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.600
No problem, Miss Yu.

07:17.840 --> 07:19.000
Second time?

07:25.840 --> 07:28.080
Master Wei's arranged a dinner banquet

07:28.160 --> 07:29.560
to thank you, Master.

07:31.200 --> 07:32.600
Please rest here for now.

07:33.400 --> 07:34.400
Thanks.

07:40.640 --> 07:43.600
WU SHIGUANG

07:47.800 --> 07:48.400
YOU CHI, LOW-RANK WEASEL DEMON

07:48.480 --> 07:49.320
So?

07:49.400 --> 07:50.440
Did I nail my act?

07:50.520 --> 07:52.520
All thanks to my majestic black smoke.

07:52.600 --> 07:54.240
Absolutely brilliant!

07:57.520 --> 07:58.520
Half a month ago,

07:59.040 --> 08:00.760
a broken-tail fox attacked Miss Yu.

08:00.840 --> 08:02.720
It must be linked
to the heart-ripping one.

08:04.120 --> 08:04.960
Otherwise,

08:05.040 --> 08:07.560
<i>those arrogant demon hunters</i>
<i>from the Shilin Sect</i>

08:07.640 --> 08:10.240
wouldn't have been guards
for an ordinary family.

08:12.800 --> 08:13.880
You Chi!

08:15.520 --> 08:16.600
Come in!

08:41.960 --> 08:43.280
Yu told me

08:43.360 --> 08:46.280
how you were kind enough
to save her half a month ago.

08:46.360 --> 08:48.440
She could've died.

08:49.320 --> 08:50.640
Thank you, Master.

08:51.400 --> 08:52.400
It was nothing.

08:57.040 --> 08:58.400
But that time,

08:59.000 --> 09:00.240
it was really dangerous.

09:01.160 --> 09:02.760
HALF A MONTH AGO

09:02.840 --> 09:03.800
Help!

09:03.880 --> 09:04.480
SEVENTH DAY OF THE TENTH MONTH

09:04.560 --> 09:05.800
Help!

09:06.640 --> 09:07.480
Help!

09:24.640 --> 09:25.560
Eight tails…

09:26.560 --> 09:27.760
A broken-tail fox!

09:29.280 --> 09:30.320
Run!

09:40.200 --> 09:41.920
That fox demon moves without a trace.

09:42.840 --> 09:43.680
Really terrifying.

09:48.240 --> 09:49.280
Shengwei,

09:49.880 --> 09:51.920
have your favorite chestnut cake.

09:52.000 --> 09:53.120
It may comfort you.

09:58.280 --> 09:59.920
Master Wu, you're truly amazing.

10:00.000 --> 10:02.160
If you hadn't chased that fox demon off,

10:02.680 --> 10:05.920
my cousin's heart
would've been ripped out too.

10:06.000 --> 10:07.640
I didn't exactly chase it off.

10:07.720 --> 10:09.920
And that day marked the first murder

10:10.000 --> 10:11.320
in this heart-ripping case.

10:11.920 --> 10:14.600
That broken-tail fox must be the culprit.

10:15.400 --> 10:17.000
It might've been hiding in this mansion,

10:17.600 --> 10:18.720
so it will try again

10:19.240 --> 10:20.240
to harm Miss Yu.

10:23.960 --> 10:26.560
Master Wu, are you serious?

10:29.720 --> 10:32.320
The air above this estate
is thick with demonic energy.

10:32.400 --> 10:34.320
I fear a high-ranking demon
has taken root here.

10:35.400 --> 10:37.920
Master Wei, if you're willing
to hire me as a house guard,

10:38.520 --> 10:40.440
I can definitely protect Miss Yu.

10:41.640 --> 10:42.800
That's great!

10:44.240 --> 10:46.640
Although Master Wu
is just a wandering hunter

10:46.720 --> 10:49.240
with no real background,

10:49.320 --> 10:52.280
although he couldn't actually defeat
the fox demon last time,

10:53.120 --> 10:56.080
although he probably still doesn't know

10:56.160 --> 10:58.240
where the fox demon is

10:58.320 --> 10:59.720
or how to guard against it,

11:01.680 --> 11:02.920
although no one knows

11:03.000 --> 11:05.240
if he could win if it does show up,

11:06.000 --> 11:07.280
one thing's sure…

11:09.760 --> 11:11.360
He's so handsome,

11:12.040 --> 11:14.120
with such a great build.

11:15.040 --> 11:19.360
Having him stay by my cousin's side,

11:19.440 --> 11:22.520
Shengwei will surely be "safe."

11:26.200 --> 11:27.400
Yeah, sure thing!

11:34.680 --> 11:35.840
Master Wu,

11:36.360 --> 11:37.680
see you later!

11:41.080 --> 11:42.600
I thought it was a sure thing,

11:43.360 --> 11:44.560
but Wei Qing has such a small mind!

11:46.440 --> 11:47.760
So petty.

11:47.840 --> 11:49.760
The one who really wants us gone

11:50.280 --> 11:51.160
isn't Wei Qing,

11:53.080 --> 11:54.160
but Miss Yu's cousin.

12:18.640 --> 12:19.600
Who's there?

12:35.600 --> 12:36.440
Rucui.

12:37.200 --> 12:38.320
Is it time yet?

12:41.760 --> 12:42.600
Rucui?

12:53.320 --> 12:54.400
Quiet.

13:17.720 --> 13:18.840
Follow my lead.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.240
Hey,

14:04.320 --> 14:05.960
are we sure this isn't dangerous?

14:06.040 --> 14:08.240
The heart thefts started on October 7th.

14:08.760 --> 14:10.680
Every seven days, someone dies.

14:11.280 --> 14:14.400
Today, the fox demon should strike again.

14:15.120 --> 14:17.360
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

14:17.960 --> 14:19.280
If you want to catch
the heart-ripping demon

14:19.360 --> 14:21.000
and claim the bounty from the Shilin Sect,

14:21.080 --> 14:22.800
then shut up, okay?

14:23.600 --> 14:26.960
So the fox demon wanted
to kill Miss Yu that day, but failed,

14:27.040 --> 14:28.600
so it killed someone else instead.

14:28.680 --> 14:30.200
Then every seven days after,

14:30.280 --> 14:31.120
it kills one person on schedule.

14:31.200 --> 14:32.200
Yeah, that's it!

14:34.120 --> 14:36.160
I'm just too smart.

14:43.200 --> 14:44.960
Are you even listening to me?

14:49.640 --> 14:50.800
Yeah.

15:06.120 --> 15:08.800
TWENTY-EIGHTH DAY OF THE TENTH MONTH
AUSPICIOUS FOR WEDDINGS

15:15.840 --> 15:17.520
Congratulations!

15:17.600 --> 15:18.880
-Congrats!
-Please, come in!

15:18.960 --> 15:19.960
Come on in!

15:20.040 --> 15:20.920
THE WELL-WOVEN HOUSE

15:21.000 --> 15:21.840
Put it over there.

15:21.920 --> 15:22.840
Right this way!

15:22.920 --> 15:24.360
Come, this way, please!

15:26.360 --> 15:27.320
What a perfect day!

15:28.240 --> 15:29.400
Congrats!

15:30.440 --> 15:32.920
Come on, right inside!

15:33.000 --> 15:34.600
THE WELL-WOVEN HOUSE

15:39.120 --> 15:40.880
The nine-tailed fox's magic
is right in my hand.

15:40.960 --> 15:41.800
JI LING

15:46.560 --> 15:48.280
LI JIE

15:48.360 --> 15:49.200
Impressive.

15:49.280 --> 15:50.320
Let's go!

15:52.320 --> 15:53.360
Alright!

15:53.440 --> 15:54.480
-Please, come in!
-Come on in!

15:54.560 --> 15:55.480
This way, please!

16:01.000 --> 16:01.920
-No need for formalities.
-Congratulations!

16:02.000 --> 16:02.840
-Please come insode.
-Congratulations!

16:03.680 --> 16:05.120
-Congrats!
-Right this way!

16:05.200 --> 16:06.160
Gentlemen,

16:06.240 --> 16:07.520
it's crowded and busy inside.

16:07.600 --> 16:08.680
Please leave your names

16:08.760 --> 16:10.360
and your wedding gifts,

16:10.880 --> 16:12.040
so I can record them properly.

16:13.760 --> 16:15.080
Well, the gifts…

16:15.160 --> 16:17.000
The gifts…

16:17.080 --> 16:17.920
Li Jie.

16:20.440 --> 16:21.360
What are you looking at me for?

16:23.640 --> 16:24.760
Congratulations.

16:30.600 --> 16:32.040
All these human customs

16:32.120 --> 16:33.400
are such a hassle.

16:34.960 --> 16:36.160
This door's flimsy.

16:36.680 --> 16:38.280
I could smash it with one swing.

16:41.280 --> 16:42.200
Rude.

16:45.520 --> 16:47.240
THE WELL-WOVEN HOUSE

16:47.320 --> 16:49.120
Oh, Master Qi!

16:49.200 --> 16:51.440
Your presence honors our humble home!

16:54.360 --> 16:56.440
-Madame Zhao, you've arrived!
-You are here.

16:56.520 --> 16:59.120
-Come in, please!
-Madame Zhao!

18:14.200 --> 18:15.520
You're not Miss Yu.

18:16.280 --> 18:17.320
Miss Yu

18:17.920 --> 18:19.840
doesn't have a vixen face like that.

18:20.440 --> 18:22.040
And you're not Master Wei.

18:22.680 --> 18:24.280
Master Wei

18:24.360 --> 18:26.440
wouldn't hold a knife to me.

18:31.640 --> 18:32.800
You're so eager?

18:35.400 --> 18:36.640
They say

18:37.360 --> 18:39.920
the first night together is priceless.

18:40.000 --> 18:41.520
How could I not be eager?

18:43.120 --> 18:45.040
Since we're now wed,

18:45.680 --> 18:46.680
then

18:47.280 --> 18:49.240
we should be open with each other!

18:54.800 --> 18:56.280
I never thought

18:56.800 --> 18:59.120
my husband would have two faces.

19:00.800 --> 19:01.760
Too bad.

19:02.520 --> 19:04.840
One woman shouldn't serve two husbands.

19:05.840 --> 19:07.000
That makes sense.

19:08.440 --> 19:09.760
So, how about

19:10.480 --> 19:12.040
you let me down first?

19:12.800 --> 19:14.160
Well then, sir,

19:15.240 --> 19:18.320
you'll have to take that dagger
away from me first.

19:30.880 --> 19:32.120
Trying to leave?

20:10.160 --> 20:12.080
Such a beautiful vase,

20:12.160 --> 20:13.200
and you have no taste for elegance.

20:13.960 --> 20:15.400
Someone as beautiful as me,

20:15.480 --> 20:17.280
and you have no taste either.

20:17.360 --> 20:19.240
Tonight, I'm divorcing you!

20:25.640 --> 20:26.520
So?

20:29.400 --> 20:30.440
Pretty clever.

20:32.560 --> 20:34.160
Isn't that Steward Luo of this family?

20:34.680 --> 20:35.840
Why is she sneaking around

20:35.920 --> 20:37.240
in her own house?

20:37.320 --> 20:38.480
Something's off.

20:39.720 --> 20:40.680
Let's check it out!

22:16.200 --> 22:17.400
Who are you?

22:18.120 --> 22:19.400
Her accomplices?

22:32.400 --> 22:33.520
What's going on?

22:40.040 --> 22:41.240
Why are you stopping me?

22:41.840 --> 22:43.000
You reek of demonic energy.

22:43.680 --> 22:44.520
You're a fox demon!

22:45.160 --> 22:47.200
She's that heart-eating demon.

22:50.320 --> 22:52.120
Heaven really is fair.

22:52.200 --> 22:54.320
It gives you such a handsome face,

22:54.400 --> 22:56.600
but no brains to go with it.

23:11.880 --> 23:12.920
Groom,

23:13.600 --> 23:15.480
why the sudden change in your face?

23:16.640 --> 23:18.800
Your opponent is me.

24:21.520 --> 24:22.600
You have no sacred power?

24:22.680 --> 24:25.400
Does that stop me from fighting you?

25:27.920 --> 25:29.440
Who exactly are you guys?

25:29.960 --> 25:32.520
I'll ask you the same question.

25:34.120 --> 25:35.800
I'm the demon hunter Wu Shiguang.

25:37.200 --> 25:39.120
Since when do demon hunters
have to worry about so much,

25:39.760 --> 25:41.080
even playing the groom?

25:41.160 --> 25:42.440
I'm pretending to be the groom

25:43.120 --> 25:44.080
for one reason only.

25:46.080 --> 25:47.040
To catch a demon.

25:51.040 --> 25:52.200
What a coincidence.

25:52.280 --> 25:53.720
We're demon hunters too.

25:53.800 --> 25:54.840
We're also here to catch demons.

25:56.000 --> 25:58.760
But unlike you back-alley,
rogue demon hunters,

25:58.840 --> 26:00.680
we're official demon hunters
from the Shilin Sect,

26:01.520 --> 26:03.680
sent here to investigate
the heart-ripping case.

26:04.560 --> 26:06.320
This is the Shilin Sect's
demon hunter commander,

26:06.400 --> 26:07.320
Li Jie.

26:10.720 --> 26:11.920
Stunned now?

26:34.160 --> 26:35.200
An ice-wielding demon.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.520
Sure enough,

26:38.040 --> 26:39.040
you're the one we're after!

26:39.880 --> 26:41.840
What grudge do we have?

26:41.920 --> 26:43.240
I don't even know you.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.480
Trying to run?

27:20.400 --> 27:21.360
It's you!

27:27.440 --> 27:28.400
Sir,

27:29.560 --> 27:30.600
save me.

27:37.200 --> 27:38.320
Let… Let her go!

27:39.320 --> 27:42.240
Sir, what's going on?

27:44.280 --> 27:45.200
Who's there?

27:53.680 --> 27:54.440
Still trying to flee?

28:37.680 --> 28:39.000
Thank you, sir, for saving me.

28:41.800 --> 28:43.000
Well…

28:43.080 --> 28:44.360
You're thanking the wrong person.

28:44.440 --> 28:46.080
The groom saved you. Thank him instead!

28:51.520 --> 28:52.720
Thank you, kind sir.

28:53.760 --> 28:54.600
You're welcome!

28:55.800 --> 28:58.040
What are those red threads made of?

29:01.720 --> 29:03.760
I guess it's blood.

29:05.240 --> 29:06.240
Submit now

29:06.760 --> 29:07.960
or die trying?

29:09.080 --> 29:10.120
It's your choice.

29:11.120 --> 29:13.000
Do I look like I'm struggling?

29:13.880 --> 29:15.440
I'm a demon hunter too,

29:15.520 --> 29:17.800
here to catch demons.
What crime have I committed?

29:17.880 --> 29:19.000
Fine.

29:20.240 --> 29:22.320
Now the whole room's
full of demon hunters, isn't it?

29:23.720 --> 29:25.200
Don't count me in.

29:26.000 --> 29:27.960
I'm no demon hunter.

29:28.040 --> 29:29.080
I'm a respectable woman.

29:30.400 --> 29:31.240
Don't bother denying it!

29:31.320 --> 29:33.520
We traced the demonic energy right here.

29:33.600 --> 29:35.440
You're the nine-tailed fox
who ripped out hearts!

29:41.880 --> 29:43.160
How terrifying!

29:43.920 --> 29:44.760
Just now,

29:45.360 --> 29:47.120
was she trying to rip out my heart?

29:48.760 --> 29:50.040
Me?

29:50.120 --> 29:51.360
A heart-eating demon?

29:52.640 --> 29:54.320
Are you joking,

29:54.840 --> 29:55.920
or serious?

29:56.000 --> 29:57.000
-I…
-Who has time

29:57.080 --> 29:58.000
to joke with a fox demon like you?

30:00.120 --> 30:02.600
You're the sect's demon hunter commander.

30:04.040 --> 30:05.120
And you?

30:05.960 --> 30:07.160
What's your identity?

30:09.480 --> 30:10.480
Me?

30:16.960 --> 30:18.000
Sir!

30:18.520 --> 30:19.360
What should I call you?

30:19.440 --> 30:20.640
My name is Ji Ling.

30:20.720 --> 30:22.760
Ji means "life's a journey,"
and Ling means "hearts that beat as one."

30:22.840 --> 30:24.280
Stay here, and don't run off, okay?

30:26.200 --> 30:27.080
Sir!

30:27.600 --> 30:29.800
Please don't leave me alone!

30:29.880 --> 30:31.760
This female demon is really terrifying!

30:32.720 --> 30:33.840
I'm so scared!

30:33.920 --> 30:35.040
So scary!

30:35.840 --> 30:36.880
So scary…

30:42.080 --> 30:42.920
You demon!

31:08.160 --> 31:10.520
LI MAO, WEDDING GUEST OF THE WEI FAMILY

31:14.880 --> 31:16.720
TAO XI, LI MAO'S WIFE

31:34.000 --> 31:35.400
Weimiao Pavilion.

31:45.440 --> 31:46.400
Blood.

32:16.200 --> 32:17.280
It's frost.

32:22.360 --> 32:23.400
It's not even winter yet.

32:24.080 --> 32:25.240
Why is there all this frost?

32:27.520 --> 32:28.560
It's demon magic.

32:39.360 --> 32:41.120
Those prayer beads are amazing.

32:41.680 --> 32:42.800
What's their story?

32:48.160 --> 32:49.200
Don't touch them.

32:52.000 --> 32:52.840
Keep them there.

32:53.760 --> 32:55.520
You're so thoughtful.

32:55.600 --> 32:56.600
Whatever you say.

32:57.360 --> 32:58.320
And you're so clever.

32:58.920 --> 33:00.480
Thanks to you tipping me off,

33:01.000 --> 33:02.840
I was able to prepare.

33:05.800 --> 33:07.040
Wangyan,

33:07.600 --> 33:09.000
the groom's a fake.

33:09.600 --> 33:11.360
He's here to catch fox demons.

33:11.960 --> 33:13.480
Be careful.

33:14.240 --> 33:15.680
Don't let him

33:16.200 --> 33:18.480
make it real or turn the tables on you.

33:20.720 --> 33:22.440
I thought we'd guarded against one,

33:22.520 --> 33:23.960
and now two more show up.

33:24.960 --> 33:26.360
That Ji Ling guy

33:27.560 --> 33:30.080
and his long-blade friend

33:30.600 --> 33:31.960
won't be easy either.

33:34.200 --> 33:36.240
But the one really hard to shake

33:36.320 --> 33:39.320
is that guy who won't let me go,
Wu Shiguang.

33:40.320 --> 33:41.360
Oh yeah?

33:43.920 --> 33:45.200
I don't believe it.

33:46.240 --> 33:47.440
Wangyan,

33:48.600 --> 33:49.720
want to make a bet?

35:39.080 --> 35:40.240
Broken-tail fox,

35:41.360 --> 35:42.440
it really is you.

36:32.520 --> 36:33.480
Miss Yu?

36:36.840 --> 36:37.760
<i>I asked you to gather some intel.</i>

36:38.720 --> 36:39.600
Did you get it all?

36:39.680 --> 36:40.800
Of course!

36:41.320 --> 36:43.480
There are 952 weasels in Luo'an City.

36:43.560 --> 36:45.480
From street gossip to corner rumors,

36:45.560 --> 36:46.480
they know everything.

36:46.560 --> 36:48.720
<i>Let's start with the bride, Miss Yu.</i>

36:48.800 --> 36:51.000
<i>She's Luo'an's famous embroiderer,</i>

36:51.080 --> 36:53.920
especially skilled
at stitching birds and beasts.

36:56.800 --> 36:58.320
<i>Now, Luo Wei.</i>

36:58.400 --> 36:59.960
<i>This woman's something else.</i>

37:00.680 --> 37:01.640
<i>A month ago,</i>

37:01.720 --> 37:03.240
<i>the Wei family's business faced a crisis,</i>

37:03.320 --> 37:04.560
<i>almost went bankrupt.</i>

37:04.640 --> 37:06.280
<i>Then Luo Wei appeared out of nowhere</i>

37:06.360 --> 37:07.600
<i>and turned things around.</i>

37:08.200 --> 37:10.000
After that, she joined the Wei mansion
and became the steward.

37:10.080 --> 37:12.240
<i>Everyone in the house</i>
<i>fears and respects her.</i>

37:12.840 --> 37:15.280
And gossip says
she's got a thing for Wei Qing.

37:15.360 --> 37:17.840
So, she really dislikes Miss Yu.

37:23.400 --> 37:24.800
As for Liu Weixue,

37:24.880 --> 37:26.280
he's Wei Qing's distant cousin.

37:27.160 --> 37:28.600
<i>The Liu family's been generals</i>
<i>for generations.</i>

37:28.680 --> 37:29.880
<i>But despite all his skill,</i>

37:29.960 --> 37:32.800
<i>Liu Weixue refuses to go to war.</i>

37:32.880 --> 37:34.200
-<i>Half a month ago,</i>
-Go…

37:34.280 --> 37:36.160
<i>he fled an arranged marriage</i>
<i>and came here.</i>

37:36.240 --> 37:37.640
-Bring the wine!
-<i>Word on the street</i>

37:37.720 --> 37:38.960
<i>is he might be interested in Luo Wei.</i>

37:39.040 --> 37:40.320
Quick, bring the medicine wine!

37:41.240 --> 37:42.080
What's all this?

37:43.240 --> 37:45.160
So lively late at night?

37:45.240 --> 37:47.760
<i>And Yu Wei grew up in the countryside,</i>

37:47.840 --> 37:49.080
<i>not from around here.</i>

37:49.160 --> 37:51.920
Their families rarely interact.

37:52.000 --> 37:53.720
So her showing up for the feast

37:54.360 --> 37:55.400
is pretty strange.

37:59.040 --> 37:59.960
Oh, quite a crowd here.

38:05.040 --> 38:06.200
Miss Yu Wei!

38:06.800 --> 38:08.080
Weren't you supposed to stay in your room?

38:08.160 --> 38:09.360
Why'd you come out?

38:09.960 --> 38:10.840
It's so dangerous!

38:13.720 --> 38:15.560
Since you called her a demon,

38:16.080 --> 38:18.800
how could I stay
in the same room with her?

38:19.800 --> 38:20.720
Plus,

38:21.320 --> 38:23.240
she totally wrecked my clothes.

38:23.760 --> 38:25.800
So I came here

38:25.880 --> 38:27.240
to change into new ones.

38:29.520 --> 38:31.160
So, sir,

38:32.360 --> 38:33.360
do I look good?

38:35.800 --> 38:37.000
Yeah… Good.

38:39.680 --> 38:40.600
What's wrong?

38:41.560 --> 38:43.600
Where's the bride I tied up?

38:44.400 --> 38:45.480
Darling,

38:46.160 --> 38:47.960
are you looking for me?

38:56.840 --> 38:58.640
I followed the broken-tail fox here.

38:59.240 --> 39:01.000
But the moment I entered this room,

39:01.520 --> 39:02.600
it vanished.

39:04.160 --> 39:05.280
What do you mean?

39:06.600 --> 39:07.880
I mean,

39:08.800 --> 39:10.200
among all of you here,

39:11.480 --> 39:12.520
one of you

39:13.360 --> 39:15.720
is the heart-ripping killer I'm after,

39:17.320 --> 39:18.840
the broken-tail fox.

39:26.520 --> 39:31.000
THE RUNAWAY FOX'S
HIDING IN THE WEI MANSION

39:31.080 --> 39:32.000
<i>Wu Wangyan,</i>

39:32.520 --> 39:34.400
<i>proceed to Luo'an at once</i>

39:35.080 --> 39:36.600
<i>and bring Xiaowei back.</i>

39:38.280 --> 39:39.240
Understood.

39:40.520 --> 39:41.760
What about me?

39:42.280 --> 39:44.680
My mission is still to assist her?

39:45.440 --> 39:46.600
<i>Your mission</i>

39:47.120 --> 39:49.760
<i>is to get close</i>
<i>to a young man named Ji Ling.</i>

39:50.880 --> 39:52.920
<i>He is your fated one.</i>

39:53.000 --> 39:54.800
Fated one?

39:57.080 --> 39:59.440
Wangyan, what does this mean?

40:03.840 --> 40:04.760
<i>You hear that?</i>

40:04.840 --> 40:06.240
All five of you

40:06.840 --> 40:07.920
are suspects!

40:08.000 --> 40:09.520
And you two

40:10.520 --> 40:11.920
are no simple cases either.

40:15.880 --> 40:17.960
Bai Ze has brought news

40:18.040 --> 40:19.280
of the nine-tailed fox, Xiaowei.

40:19.360 --> 40:20.280
SHILIN SECT, SCALE CAVE

40:20.360 --> 40:23.320
Right now, she's hiding
in the Wei mansion in Luo'an.

40:25.600 --> 40:26.480
Li Jie,

40:27.320 --> 40:29.360
it's time to bring her back.

40:30.600 --> 40:31.440
Understood.
